title: Person of Interest - 5x02 'SNAFU' - Wake Her Up
author: POISuit
comment: best show ever... great cast, I'll miss them

It is so sad to see, that John has lost his entire family. I loved everything about this scene from the music to the Times Square set. POI was truly ahead of its time. It is a damn shame that it never got a big following as Westworld. I miss this show so much.
